c <- 300000000
h <- 6.626*(10^-34)
Q <- 1.602*(10^-19)
nm.to.m <- function(nm) {
  m <- (nm*(10^-9))
  return(m)}

Frequency.Photon <- function(m) {
  v <- (c/m)
  return(v)}

Photon.Energy <- function(v) {
  D.E. <- (h*v)
  return(D.E.)}

j.to.ev <- function(D.E.) {
  eV <- (D.E./Q)
  return(eV)}

Photon.Energy(Frequency.Photon(nm.to.m(300)))
[1] 6.626e-19
elec <- function(x){
  vo.2 <- (j.to.ev(Photon.Energy(Frequency.Photon(nm.to.m(x)))))
  return(vo.2)}

 T <- function(x){
  Transmittance <- (1/(10^(abs(x))))
  return(Transmittance)}
